f the Physical Card to be authorized., processing_category: map{category!: str, refund: map{original_card_payment_id: str}} # Fields specific to a specific type of authorization, such as Automatic Fuel Dispensers, Refund Authorizations, or Cash Disbursements., terminal_id: str # The terminal identifier (commonly abbreviated as TID) of the terminal the card is transacting with.}
